# Trivy ignore list for VarLens-IaC.
#
# The Concept Pilot accepts the CVEs listed here because they are upstream
# Go stdlib issues in the Compose stack images (caddy, louislam/uptime-kuma,
# amir20/dozzle) — fixable only via image rebuild by the upstream
# maintainers.
#
# Mitigation in this configuration:
#   - Caddy basic_auth is the only entry point to Kuma/Dozzle
#   - Concept Pilot is intranet-only, self-signed TLS
#   - §vertrag5 real-data lock: only test data permitted
#   - Stage 2 will either bump or replace Kuma/Dozzle
#
# Review obligation: every three months (see expiration date in the exp:
# annotation). On image tag bump in compose/docker-compose.yml, Check
# which CVEs the new tag still has and only keep the remaining ones.
#
# As of: 2026-04-29 — next review: 2026-07-29.

